567
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:29,560
That Yin woman works as a TV anchor.

568
00:29:29,760 --> 00:29:31,240
I can't be bothered to care about him.

569
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,880
We each do our own thing.

570
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,440
