575
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:43,840
Yesterday, I heard she died in Xinhua Lane.

576
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:45,040
It gave me quite a scare.

577
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:46,040
By midnight,

578
00:29:46,080 --> 00:29:48,160
