579
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,640
He rushed back overnight.

580
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,840
Nothing anyone says matters.

581
00:29:50,840 --> 00:29:52,320
The reason I went to her office

582
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,320
was to look around

583
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:55,440
to see if there was anything about the two of us.

584
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:57,440
I searched all over,

585
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:59,120
but found nothing.

586
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:00,240
I didn't take anything.

587
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:01,160
Didn't take anything.

