589
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:03,960
Three o'clock.

590
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:05,720
Just a little after three.

591
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:09,640
Does this painting look familiar?

592
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:13,280
Yes, yes.

593
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:15,760
Familiar, familiar. There's another painting too.

594
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:17,040
Don't try to fool me.

595
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:18,480
What did you bring back?

596
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,520
I didn't pay attention.

597
00:30:24,840 --> 00:30:25,840
Brought a painting.

598
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:28,840
Why would a big boss like you steal a painting?

599
00:30:30,760 --> 00:30:31,840
This painting is—

600
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:35,440
I bought it at an auction to give to her.

601
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,440
I was afraid of exposing our relationship.

602
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,840
Besides, I paid for it myself.

603
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:42,680
So this can't be considered stealing, right?

604
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,560
Whose painting is it?

605
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:46,840
I don't remember.

606
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:48,760
Yin Hui liked it.

607
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:49,720
So I gave it to her.

608
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:51,600
Anyway, it was pretty expensive.

609
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:53,560
Which auction was it?

610
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:56,280
How would I know what the painting was for?

611
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:57,320
He acted like a thief.

612
00:30:57,320 --> 00:30:59,320
He hid in that room and tore up the painting.

613
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:15,840
He shredded those papers.

614
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:17,840
Bag.

615
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:28,760
It's all here.

616
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:33,680
That little brat died mysteriously at his place.

617
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,080
A human life is at stake.

618
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:36,640
What if it drags me and my dad into this?

619
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,840
Right?

620
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:38,840
These

621
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:41,160
are records of Tian Haisheng and that woman

622
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,760
colluding over the years

623
00:31:42,960 --> 00:31:45,240
to use Haisheng Charity to make money.

624
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:47,440
First, they find people in need of donations.

625
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:48,640
Then Yin Hui

626
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:50,560
reports their stories.

627
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:53,040
Then they use the Haisheng Charity platform to raise funds.

628
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:55,040
After the recipients get the donations,

629
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:57,640
they widely publicize their good deeds.

630
00:31:57,840 --> 00:31:59,440
This way, they gain a good reputation through deception.

631
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,240
Then they use various methods

632
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:03,880
to force the recipients to give up most of the donations.

633
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,280
Those people,

634
00:32:05,280 --> 00:32:08,040
just to get some money, have no choice but to agree.

635
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:10,560
If they refuse, they get retaliated against.

636
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:13,640
That woman would use the media to spread rumors.

637
00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:15,640
She'd say the recipients' stories are fake.

638
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:17,480
Look at this.

639
00:32:18,280 --> 00:32:20,080
This wasteful woman.

640
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:21,440
Watch your language.

641
00:32:21,560 --> 00:32:22,680
If I'd known it would turn out like this,

642
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,040
I never should've gotten involved with Yin Hui.

643
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:26,920
She's so scheming.

644
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:29,880
She kept a record of every transaction.

645
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:31,960
She was planning to keep something as leverage.

646
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:33,040
Officer,

647
00:32:33,280 --> 00:32:35,040
she threatened me, saying

648
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:37,240
if I dared to break up, she'd send me to jail.

649
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:41,080
I-I-I went to her office

650
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:42,760
just to

651
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:45,720
get these records back.

652
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:47,760
In the end, I still got caught.

653
00:32:47,760 --> 00:32:49,960
She brought all this on herself.

654
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,520
She deserved to die.

655
00:32:53,760 --> 00:32:56,840
Yes, I painted this for Yin Hui.

