00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:58,560
Are you close with Yin Hui?

657
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:01,680
I heard you never sell your paintings.

658
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,000
Or give them away.

659
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:03,640
Not close.

660
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:06,560
We have some mutual social connections.

661
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:07,640
We've met a few times.

662
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:10,640
She kept asking me to paint something for her.

663
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:12,880
She mentioned it several times.

664
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:15,640
If I keep refusing, it would be embarrassing.

665
00:33:16,080 --> 00:33:16,920
I see.

666
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:19,680
Sorry for the trouble, Teacher Zhao.

667
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,480
Sorry to disturb you so late.

668
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:22,560
I'll be leaving now.

669
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,240
No need to see me out.

