673
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:58,040
The person involved had this name.

674
00:33:58,760 --> 00:33:59,920
Let me look it up.

675
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,560
Found it.

676
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:07,360
Two years ago, Qin Yang

677
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:10,080
