683
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:27,240
The charity organization was called Haisheng Charity.

684
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:29,320
Yin Hui faked donations.

685
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:31,040
Framed a good person.

686
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:32,760
Qin Yang, because of this incident,

687
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,280
